<subSubSection pageId="30" pageNumber="1285" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="30.[178,1086,857,1387]" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">
The subspecies is widely distributed in the eastern part of the West Palaearctic from southeastern Europe to north westernmost 
<collectingCountry box="[625,685,1307,1329]" name="China" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">China</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[701,793,1307,1329]" country="China" name="Xinjiang Uygur" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">Xinjiang</collectingRegion>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="JAEGER B" box="[816,1086,1307,1328]" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285" pagination="397 - 406" refId="ref36783" refString="JAEGER B. &amp; B. M. KATAEV (2003): Carabidae: Harpalini: Subtribe Stenolophina. Pp. 397 - 406. - In: LOBL I. &amp; A. SMETANA (eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera, Vol. 1. Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Stenstrup: Apollo Books, 819 pp." type="book chapter" year="2003">JAEGER &amp; KATAEV 2003:</bibRefCitation>
405; KATAEV &amp; KABAK 2014: 250). It is firstly recorded here for 
<collectingCountry box="[869,936,1336,1358]" name="Jordan" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">Jordan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[990,1082,1336,1358]" name="Lebanon" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">Lebanon</collectingCountry>
. First detailed records for 
<collectingCountry box="[434,520,1365,1387]" name="Pakistan" pageId="30" pageNumber="1285">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
are also provided.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
